<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhè shì shén zhù fú de de fāng, chōng mǎn nà càn làn de yáng guāng.
 huāng qiū yǐ biàn chéng cuì lǜ de shān gǎng, shā mò yǐ yǒu hé shuǐ liú tǎng.
 yīn wèi chūn tiān yǐ jīng lái dào, de shàng bǎi huā qí fàng.
 zhǔ de pú táo yuán zhèng kāi huā fàng xiāng, wǒ men yào huān hū gē chàng.
 shén de ér nǚ nǐ yào gāng qiáng, shén de ér nǚ nǐ yào shǒu wàng.
 zhǔ yào fù xìng zhè gè de fāng, tā de zhǐ yì wú rén néng zǔ dǎng.</lyrics>
<title>zhè shì shén zhù fú de de fāng 迦南1168</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1168</hymn_number>
</song>